ort stated fisher had taken multiple drugs prior to her death she was  “i am not shocked that part of her health was affected by drugs” her brother told the ap “if you want to know what killed her it’s all of it” fisher explored her issues with addiction in her  bestselling semiautobiographical novel postcards from the edge which was later turned into a movie starring meryl streep “i couldn’t stop or stay stopped it was never my fantasy to have a drug problem” she told people in  “i’d say ‘oh f— it i haven’t done anything for a couple of months why not let’s celebrate not doing them by doing them’ i got into trouble each time i hated myself i just beat myself up it was very painful” she told people in  “the only lesson for me or anybody is that you have to get help i’m not embarrassed” show full article most popular  jada pinkett smith wishes those rumors about her and will smith being swingers were true  johnny depp allegedly spent  on a couch from keeping up with the kardashians for his daughter lilyrose  kevin hart laughs at ‘bs’ allegations he cheated on pregnant wife eniko parrish  brooklyn beckham is dating singer and youtube star madison beer  jada pinkett smith says she was a drug dealer when she met tupac shakur see also send to email address your name your email address cancel post was not sent  check your email addresses email check failed please try again sorry your blog cannot share posts by email thermo fisher todd hewitt broth  bioz  ratings for lifescience research products antibodies kits cloning pcr crispr elisa proteins rnai cells vectors about about us news team advisors ambassadors bioz stars bioz vstars sign in home  search results  thermo fisher  todd hewitt broth loading about bioz about us   team   advisors   bioz stars   bioz vstars   news join our bioz ambassador program partner with usjoin our vendor partner community subscribe to data analytics reports our platform bioz is the worlds first search engine for life science experimentation t