ortable and the music is usually dialedin to awesome american soul and jazz tracks that are several layers more interesting than the junkfood pop that permeates many places if youre considering giving him a try dont hesitate he gives the best mens cut in austin ive found in two decades of living here ive been going to todd for maybe two years now  since before the mueller shop  and cant imagine going anywhere else i tried a couple other premier mens barber shops before finding todd and never found the attention to detail i find here i especially love that he meticulously ensures the sidesback fade evenly an issue ive had in the past while his prior location was closer to where i live  work the new shop has a great vibe and is much more my style todd is very personable which is always great but he will also let me just sit there and think which i appreciate very much the ability to schedule online is a great perk as well todd says hes a perfectionist to a fault but if youre cutting hair the way he does it you kind of need to be he takes his time every time ive never seen anyone blend the sides of my hair by hand and so meticulously if you are worried about not being able to style your hair every day as good as he does it let him know and hell give you a little styling lesson also how has nobody mentioned the free whiskey  i have been looking for a great mens haircut in austin since i moved from chicago todd is the guy he does a wonderful job wth my hair and spends the time needed to get it perfect shop is clean and everyone there is friendly scheduling system is easy to use i would recommend todd to anyone who is looking for a great haircut and good conversation while he is doing it this is the best haircut youll ever get the reviews are real the barbers are great and this shop is my hands down favorite barber in the us sirjoe entertained me with witty barber banter while meticulously going through my difficult hair adding character with each snip go to floyds if you